00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Crème pâtissière or Pastry cream

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:27.000
To make Crème pâtissière or Pastry cream, you will need:

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:35.000
milk, sugar, egg yolks, cornstarch and vanilla extract.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:41.000
First bring milk just up to the boil.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:05.000
Meanwhile, mix together egg yolks, sugar, cornstarch and vanilla extract.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:13.000
Whisk egg yolks and sugar until you reach a pale creamy consistency.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:34.000
Stir in cornstarch and whisk well.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:07.000
Finally, add vanilla extract and mix.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:27.000
Gradually whisk some boiling milk into egg yolk mixture to make it a bit more liquid.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:56.000
Then return to saucepan and cook, whisking constantly until thick.

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:32.000
Cook over medium heat until boiling for 3 min, whisking constantly.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:52.000
Then transfer to stainless steel tray to cool and refrigerate.

